<item>
            <title>[LU-15814] node.yml files have wrong distro when almalinux is tested</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15814</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &amp;lt;node&amp;gt;.yml files written by the test framework contain the wrong distribution when running an almalinux test, these in turn are uploaded to maloo and they&apos;re incorrectly tagged as centos, see example below:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;Build:&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;&#160; &#160; lbats_build_id:&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;&#160; &#160; lbats_build_name:&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;&#160; &#160; architecture: x86_64&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;&#160; &#160; os: GNU/Linux&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;&#160; &#160; os_distribution: &lt;font color=&quot;#FF0000&quot;&gt;CentOS 8.5&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;&#160; &#160; version: 2.14.0.ddn41&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;&#160; &#160; build: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b_es6_0/310&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b_es6_0/310&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;&#160; &#160; branch: b_es6_0&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;&#160; &#160; revision: 4b8c7f2183836b652d912dce1d5ec16a5e1fe453&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;&#160; &#160; kernel_version: 4.18.0-348.7.1.el8_5.x86_64&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;&#160; &#160; file_system: NA&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
